Code: EXEC SQL SELECT T1.COD_TP_LANCDOCF, T1.DT_INIVIG_LANCDOCF, T1.VALOR_LANCAMENTO, T2.DESCRICAO_LANCDOCF, T2.ABREV_LANCDOCF FROM SEGUROS.FI_PAGA_DOCF_LANC T1, SEGUROS.FI_PAGA_DOCF_LANC T2 WHERE T1.NUM_DOCF_INTERNO = :NUM_DOCF_INTERNO AND T1.COD_TP_LANCDOCF = T2.COD_TP_LANCDOCF AND T1.DT_INIVIG_LANCDOCF = T2.DT_INIVIG_LANCDOCF ORDER BY T1.COD_TP_LANCDOCF END SQL
